    <summary>A program to manage the Windows right-click context menu.</summary>
    <description>A program to manage the Windows right-click context menu.

## Screenshot

![Screenshot](https://cdn.statically.io/gh/Aurocosh/chocolatey-packages/master/automatic/context-menu-manager/img/screenshot.png)

## Key features

* Enable and disable context menu options for files, folders, submenus (e.g. open, send to), Internet Explorer, and Win+X
* Modify menu names and icons
* Delete context menu entries
* Navigate menus in the registry or File Explorer
* Add custom menu items and commands

## Supported systems

* Windows Vista, 7, 8, 8.1, 10
* 32 and 64 bit operating systems
* Support for display scaling, optimal at 150% DPI
* Localization support

This package installs the .NET 3.5 build (`ContextMenuManager.NET.3.5.exe`) and requires the [.NET Framework 3.5](https://community.chocolatey.org/packages/DotNet3.5) feature on Windows 8 and later.
